name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: External Ids for this item.

name: $serviceCategory
desc: Returns: A broad categorization of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

name: $addserviceCategory
desc: A broad categorization of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: A broad categorization of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

name: $serviceType
desc: Returns: The type of appointments that can be booked into this slot (ideally this would be an identifiable service - which is at a location, rather than the location itself). If provided then this overrides the value provided on the availability resource.

name: $addserviceType
desc: The type of appointments that can be booked into this slot (ideally this would be an identifiable service - which is at a location, rather than the location itself). If provided then this overrides the value provided on the availability resource.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The type of appointments that can be booked into this slot (ideally this would be an identifiable service - which is at a location, rather than the location itself). If provided then this overrides the value provided on the availability resource.

name: $specialty
desc: Returns: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.

name: $addspecialty
desc: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.

name: $appointmentType
desc: Returns: The style of appointment or patient that may be booked in the slot (not service type).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The style of appointment or patient that may be booked in the slot (not service type).

name: $schedule
desc: Returns: The schedule resource that this slot defines an interval of status information.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The schedule resource that this slot defines an interval of status information.

name: $status
desc: Returns: busy | free | busy-unavailable | busy-tentative | entered-in-error.

name: $start
desc: Returns: Date/Time that the slot is to begin.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Date/Time that the slot is to begin.

name: $end
desc: Returns: Date/Time that the slot is to conclude.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Date/Time that the slot is to conclude.

name: $overbooked
desc: Returns: This slot has already been overbooked, appointments are unlikely to be accepted for this time.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: This slot has already been overbooked, appointments are unlikely to be accepted for this time.

name: $comment
desc: Returns: Comments on the slot to describe any extended information. Such as custom constraints on the slot.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Comments on the slot to describe any extended information. Such as custom constraints on the slot.
